# The app image does `COPY . /app` (Dockerfile), so anything here that is NOT excluded is baked into
# image layers — including any pushed image. Operator secrets and local state MUST stay out:
#   - .panella/ holds the 0600 approval token + governance overlay that `panella init` provisions;
#     baking them into the image would defeat the whole secret boundary (Codex B1 P1).
#   - .env holds PANELLA_API_KEY (the internal service secret) — never in an image layer.
.panella/
.env

# Local dev state / caches — not part of the shipped image, keep layers small + reproducible.
.git/
.gitignore
.venv/
**/__pycache__/
*.pyc
.ruff_cache/
.pytest_cache/
.*-evidence/
dist/
build/
*.egg-info/
